last week or so. Hardware is being upgraded as quickly<BR>
as possible (you don't buy high-end router upgrades at<BR>
your local computer store, you know :)<BR><BR>
I think overall our downtime has been VERY minimal,<BR>
especially in the last couple of months. I realize though<BR>
that's it's still very frustrating to not be able to play one<BR>
night when you were planning on it, and we apologize for<BR>
the inconvenience.</FONT><BR><BR></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>	
